---
title: Sweet Thai Chili Turkey Lettuce Wraps with Zesty Veggies & Peanuts
description: Craving a meal with some crunch? You could certainly add potato chips to dinner (no judgment here), but we’ve got something a little more colorful in mind. These wraps feature ground pork cooked in a sweet chili sauce and a sweet rainbow salad made with cucumber, radishes, carrots, and pickled red onion. Once you’ve divided everything between crisp romaine leaves, you’ll top it all off with peanuts for even more texture. What time is it? Crunch time!
